                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d762">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Meyer</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-07-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 18, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Meyer advises that the Standard Oil Company should immediately bring suit
                    for damages against the Russian Government. The signature of the telegram giving
                    power of attorney to the lawyer with right of substitution should be legalized
                    by a Russian consul with a statement that the act is made according to the laws
                    of the country.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
